info.title: Project - Read
info.description: The service reads data from the project using Project Internal ID, and can retrieve project header data as well as description fields, organizational fields and planned date fields. You can use the WBS Element entity type to get details about the WBS Elements associated with this project.

x-sap-shortText: Read Project data using this synchronous inbound service
